<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ol>
      <li><p>Elena and Han ran the same distance. <m>\frac{3}{6}</m>  and <m>\frac{1}{2}</m>  are the same distance from the starting point.</p>   <p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158761.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158761.svg" width="80%"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158762.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158762.svg" width="80%"/></li>
      <li><p>Jada and Kiran ran the same distance. <m>\frac{1}{4}</m> and <m>\frac{2}{8}</m> are the same distance from 0. </p>  <p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158759.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158759.svg" width="80%"/></li>
      <li><p>Lin and Mai didn't run the same distance because <m>\frac{5}{6}</m> is not at the same location on the number line as <m>\frac{2}{3}</m>. </p>  <p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158763.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158763.svg" width="80%"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158764.svg"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Expand image" src="../../../../../assets/expand-9ef5655e2d1b5ba286de1390c97f4243f15e264c89106027f5d071073ab562bb.png" title="Expand image"/><p>[@@@@@@@@] WARNING: Fix Image.</p><img alt="Number line." role="image" src="../../../../../../figures/tikz-file-158764.svg" width="80%"/></li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


